Israel Sapiens Rises Most in Two Months After Merger Plans

-- B y   R o n i t   G o o d m a n
-- 
2011-03-22T14:57:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/israel-sapiens-rises-most-in-two-months-after-merger-plans-1-.html
Sapiens International Corp. N.V.
surged the most in more than two months after the information-
technology company said it signed a non-binding term sheet for a
merger with FIS Software Ltd. and IDIT I.D.I. Technologies Ltd.  The shares rallied 8.3 percent, the biggest gain since Jan.
17, to 14.59 shekels at the 4:30 p.m. close in  Tel Aviv .  The terms give FIS Software and IDIT I.D.I. an aggregate
value of about $75 million, the company said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ronit Goodman in Tel Aviv at 
